Michael Spellman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Spellman 0 Michael Spellman (born November 19, 1978) is an American film, television and stage actor. He appeared in the movie Charlie Wilson's War and on the TV shows How I Met Your Mother, ER and Lie to Me.
